<lyrics>[V1]
 1-(ḥạjty dwmạaⁿ ạ̹lyk rạḥty fy rạḥtyk
 kl ạ̉mry fy ydyk ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- ḥbyby yạ yswʿ .ṭbyby yạ yswʿ .nṣyby yạ yswʿ
 wḥdk mlʾ ạlḍlwʿ
 2-(ḥbk rby ktẖyr wạldm ạljạry gẖzyr
 ṣfḥk ʿny ktẖyr ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2
 3-(lst ạ̉ḥtạk swạl qlt ly ạ̉fgẖrn fạk
 ạ̉nt tmlạ̉ ftạk ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2
 4-(ạ̉nt sydy ḥbyby ạ̉nt ly kẖyr nṣyb
 ạ̉nt ật ʿn qryb ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2</lyrics>
<title>ḥạjty dwmaⁿạ</title>
</song>